title: Jenkins And Jonez - Back to school
itunes:title: Jenkins And Jonez - Back to school
description:
The guys get ready for school to start back up by reminiscing about when they were younger and how they got ready for the first day, floating over 40 miles in a pumpkin, how difficult it is to be a Lakers fan and is this the end for Russell Westbrook in Lala Land? #Herd
